  <brief_title>Efficacy and Tolerability Study of Device, RD047-26 for the Treatment of Mild to Moderate Atopic Dermatitis in Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Pilot Study to Determine the Efficacy and Tolerability of a Device, RD047-26 for the Treatment of Mild to Moderate Atopic Dermatitis With Associated Pruritus in Adults</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
