    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out if investigational device, RD047-26, is safe and
      useful for the treatment of mild to moderate atopic dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      RD047-26, a device, may be tolerable and effective for the treatment of mild to moderate
      atopic dermatitis with associated pruritus in adults. The treatment effect will be evaluated
      by the subject and investigator.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
